Have some water.

369
00:26:22,467 --> 00:26:24,320
I'm hungry for food.

370
00:26:24,726 --> 00:26:25,360
Oh.

371
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:54,209
Can I borrow your phone, please?

372
00:26:56,590 --> 00:26:58,280
I'm going to call my dad to come pick me up.

373
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:04,560
Hey, Noey.

374
