540
00:39:45,058 --> 00:39:46,360
You can pick your bed first.

541
00:39:46,836 --> 00:39:47,560
Oh.

542
00:39:47,649 --> 00:39:49,000
You can choose first.

543
00:39:49,532 --> 00:39:51,440
Whichever bed you pick,

544
00:39:51,476 --> 00:39:53,200
