545
00:39:55,267 --> 00:39:57,120
Then, I'll take this one.

546
00:39:58,523 --> 00:39:59,040
Alright.

547
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,516
I'll take this one then.

548
00:40:03,987 --> 00:40:06,000
We each get our own locker.

549
00:40:06,369 --> 00:40:09,643
